INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE (((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsReceivedCandidate] = 0)

SELECT [p].[ProjectId], [p].[CandidateId], [p].[StartDate], CASE
    WHEN [p].[IsRunning] = 1
    THEN GETDATE() ELSE [p].[EndDate]
END AS [EndDate], [p].[ProjectTitle], [p].[ProjectCompany], [p].[ProjectLocation], [p].[Description], [p].[IsRunning]
FROM [Candidate].[Project] AS [p]
WHERE [p].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_3
ORDER BY [p].[EndDate] DESC, [p].[StartDate] DESC

FROM [Candidate].[EducationalBackground] AS [eb]

SELECT TOP(1) [m].[CandidateId], [m].[CompanyId], [m].[IsReceivedCandidate]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE (((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsReceivedCandidate] = 0)
